40' class='bbp-action bbp-retweet-action' title='Retweet'><span><em style='margin-left: 1em;'></em><strong>Retweet</strong></span></a><a href='https://twitter.com/intent/favorite?tweet_id=324500698370826240' class='bbp-action bbp-favorite-action' title='Favorite'><span><em style='margin-left: 1em;'></em><strong>Favorite</strong></span></a></div><div style='float:left; padding:0; margin:0'><a href='http://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=carlosgr_arahat'><img style='width:48px; height:48px; padding-right:7px; border:none; background:none; margin:0' src='http://a0.twimg.com/profile_images/3520196598/65b8c8301bb7181df30ff6c226d4eee3_normal.jpeg' /></a></div><div style='float:left; padding:0; margin:0'><a style='font-weight:bold' href='http://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=carlosgr_arahat'>@carlosgr_arahat</a><div style='margin:0; padding-top:2px'>Carlos Gustavo Ruiz</div></div><div style='clear:both'></div></div></div></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><style type='text/css'>#bbpBox_324502059888046080 a { text-decoration:none; color:#BD9A5E; }#bbpBox_324502059888046080 a:hover { text-decoration:underline; }</style><div id='bbpBox_324502059888046080' class='bbpBox' style='padding:20px; margin:5px 0; background-color:#B5B18A; background-image:url(http://a0.twimg.com/profile_background_images/778538975/c1a1fec13c3046047f906054bbac65a8.jpeg);'><div style='background:#fff; padding:10px; margin:0; min-height:48px; color:#333333; -moz-border-radius:5px; -webkit-border-radius:5px;'><span style='width:100%; font-size:18px; line-height:22px;'>8vo. concretar logros individuales y de peque&#241;os equipos ser&#225; fundamental para resistir los embates de las guada&#241;as econ&#243;micas y pol&#237;ticas.</span><div class='bbp-actions' style='font-size:12px; width:100%; padding:5px 0; margin:0 0 10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e6e6e6;'><img align='middle' src='http://arah.at/wp-content/plugins/twitter-blackbird-pie//images/bird.png' /><a title='tweeted on 17 April, 20